{"tid":1240782,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"作為青年人，林鄭媽媽你知唔知我其實想點","createTime":"2019-06-18T12:48:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T15:23:02.000Z","uid":235407,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dff58e4e073bbcc74643b7c694de7a024c70f2e6","tid":1240782,"uid":235407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T12:48:02.000Z","msg":"睇完今日記招，都唔知講咩好喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實林鄭媽媽你咁想同青年人同行，你知唔知我地想點先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實呢，你以為我地青年人好中意罷工罷市罷課山長水遠出去政總野餐咩；你又以為我地每個星期日係屎忽痕，所以先去行幾個鐘街咩；唔通我地成一百萬二百萬零一人出尼，係因為想威想疊馬同埋英雄主意咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係呀，林鄭媽媽，唔需要咁為我地著想而迫我地出尼曬下太陽做下運動出下汗。我呢，其實想做翻個廢青咋。我想每日夜晚可以得閒睇愛回家，想weekend毒係屋企煲下動漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你知唔知我動漫進度落後左幾多呀？你知唔知我幾多日無心情入game消體呀？<br />\n林鄭媽媽，如果想同行，不如一齊睇下動漫啦。我推介可以睇下魯魯修丫，佢嘅政治手段可能有小小偏激或者誇張，但係幾值得你學習架，佢都係首先引起公憤然後再&hellip;<br />\n林鄭媽媽，俾我地抖下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"689c2492d98de91bd1503583e956dae5dce25d95","tid":1240782,"uid":4458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T12:50:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢知就唔會咁on9啦"},{"pid":"de77b5e1f3bc6bf4cc76299db3f34cc3c7425e9a","tid":1240782,"uid":235407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"689c2492d98de91bd1503583e956dae5dce25d95","tid":1240782,"uid":4458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T12:50:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢知就唔會咁on9啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T13:01:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c633f9e44ba22e77bac04783fde8b9b94971f2b7","tid":1240782,"uid":236878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"689c2492d98de91bd1503583e956dae5dce25d95","tid":1240782,"uid":4458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T12:50:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢知就唔會咁on9啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T13:08:05.000Z","msg":"你兩個天真過天真嬌喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"303dd22cc7e1d5ae99322664ab5728cbbb090794","tid":1240782,"uid":235407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T15:23:02.000Z","msg":"想當年啲同學話睇gundam seed學英文架：freedom &amp; justice<br />\n大家唔好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只少我地嘅政府唔識呢兩個英文生字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}